# Backup Account
#
# This account serves as the centralized hub for backup and disaster recovery:
# - AWS Backup (cross-account backup management)
# - Backup vaults with cross-account access
# - Organization backup policies
# - Disaster recovery automation
# - Backup compliance monitoring
# - Cross-region backup replication
#
# Benefits:
# - Centralized backup management across all accounts
# - Consistent backup policies and retention
# - Enhanced security through account isolation
# - Simplified compliance and auditing
# - Cost optimization through centralized storage
